211
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,480
Thank you, Your Majesty
and Your Highness.

212
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:25,480
I assigned the crown prince
to East Office

213
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,030
to take charge of all the criminal cases

214
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,000
in Liang

215
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,790
