of Lady Wuxue's death

260
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,870
and clearing Ji Yun's name.

261
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:12,670
Your Majesty,

262
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,630
Feng's grown up

263
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,240
